<section class="mt-32 w-1/2 mx-auto">
  <h2 class="font-extrabold text-5xl tracking-tight">
    Your questions, Answered
  </h2>
  <div class="mt-12">
    <div class="mt-6">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium">General</h3>
      <p class="font-medium text-gray-900 mt-4">What is Relay?</p>
      <p class="mt-2 leading-5 text-gray-600">
        <span class="block mb-2">Relay is Zimbabwe's long-distance ride-sharing platform.</span>
        <span class="block mb-2">We connect drivers who have empty seats with passengers travelling the same route.</span>
        <span class="block mb-2">Instead of empty cars or unpredictable hitchhiking, drivers and passengers can plan their journeys in advance, hours or days before departure.</span>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-6 hidden">
      <h3 class="font-bold text-base text-black-800">Can a driver or passenger fail to show up?</h3>
      <p class="mt-2">
        It's rare. <br>
        To keep the platform reliable, we apply small commitment fee. Passengers pay a small booking fee, and drivers pay to access ride requests. This helps reduce fake trips and last-minute cancellations
        We also use automated checks to detect and filter suspicious activity before it appears on the platform.<br>
        Drivers and passengers who repeatedly fail to show up may be suspended.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8 ">
<details class="group border-t border-gray-200 py-6">
  <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none font-medium text-2xl [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
    For drivers
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width="20"
      height="20"
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      fill="none"
      stroke="currentColor"
      stroke-width="2"
      stroke-linecap="round"
      stroke-linejoin="round"
      class="transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180"
    >
      <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/>
    </svg>
  </summary>
  <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600 space-y-4">
    <div>
      <p class="font-medium text-gray-900">Do I need to change my plans?</p>
      <p>No. You only list trips you’re already taking, Relay just helps you fill empty seats and save on fuel and tollgate costs.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="font-medium text-gray-900">How do payments work?</p>
      <p>Passengers place a small commitment to secure their seat. This helps avoid no-shows, and you receive the agreed amount for the trip. 
        You also pay a small commitment fee for the trip.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="font-medium text-gray-900">How does the driver commitment fee work?</p>
      <p>When a passenger requests your ride, 
        you pay a once-off $1 to unlock their details and accept or decline.
        If more passengers request the same trip, those are free.
        </p>
    </div>    

    <div>
      <p class="font-medium text-gray-900">What if no one books my ride?</p>
      <p>Nothing changes. You still take your trip as planned, there’s no risk in listing.</p>
    </div>




How does the driver commitment fee work?


  </div>
</details>

<details class="group border-t border-gray-200 border-b py-6">
  <summary class="flex items-center justify-between cursor-pointer list-none font-medium text-2xl [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden">
    For passengers
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      width="20"
      height="20"
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      fill="none"
      stroke="currentColor"
      stroke-width="2"
      stroke-linecap="round"
      stroke-linejoin="round"
      class="transition-transform duration-300 group-open:rotate-180"
    >
      <path d="M6 9l6 6 6-6"/>
    </svg>
  </summary>
  <div class="mt-4 text-gray-600 space-y-4">
    <div>
      <p class="font-medium text-gray-900">How do I find a ride?</p>
      <p>Search your route, choose a driver, and request a seat. It takes less than a minute.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="font-medium text-gray-900">Why is there a commitment payment?</p>
      <p>A small commitment of 50cents secures your seat and shows the driver you’re serious. It helps reduce cancellations and keeps rides reliable.</p>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="font-medium text-gray-900">Can I trust the driver?</p>
      <p>You can view driver details, car info and after booking, and you can still decide to cancel if you don't feel safe or if something feels off to you.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  </div>
</section>


